776
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:11,680
Li.

777
00:40:12,919 --> 00:40:13,720
Li.

778
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,800
Good.

779
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:15,959
Li.

780
00:40:15,959 --> 00:40:17,119
